</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>The Caughnawaga Indians arrived at Cambridge on 20 January. See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0127" class="document">GW to Hancock, 24 Jan. 1776.</a></p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>The letter-book copy in <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span> includes here the words of a like nature.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0003">3</a>
	
   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0529" class="document">GW to William Howe, 18 Dec.</a>, and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0543" class="document">Howe to GW, 21 Dec. 1775.</a></p>

</div>
<span class="pb center" title="page number in print edition (no page scan available)" id="GEWN-03-03-02-pb-0114">[114]</span>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0004">4</a>

   <p>Henry Knox arrived at Cambridge on 18 January.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0005-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0005">5</a>

   <p>David Wooster wrote to Schuyler from Montreal on 18 Dec. 1775: General Montgomery informs me that You desired me to send You an Account of the Number of Men that I discharged between Albany &amp; Tyonderoga, Therefore I would inform You that I did not discharge any Men but only gave them a Furlough &amp; that to the Connecticut Troops only, to pass to New England, as the Term of their Inlistment were not expired &amp; I imagined they might be very serviceable there (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span>).</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0006-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0079-fn-0006">6</a>

   <p>The letter-book copy in <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span> reads the service they were upon.</p>

</div>
